The Project has received BU Permission vide PRM/DABHODA/225/07/2013/3704/2017 dated 25/07/2017. The project is has received occupancy certificate dated 25/07/2017, hence the requirement of maintaining separate RERA Account is done away with vide Circular no 2/2017 dated 29/07/2017. For the process of RERA Returns the existing bank account is shown as RERA Account. The statement of the same is attached herewith. Present RERA Approval of the aforesaid project is in Phased Manner i.e. only commercial units are constructed and approved hence this certificate is towards % completion of 56 commercial units only as per approved Lay out plan. As informed to us the there are no transactions between April and August 19, the last entry made in books of account is up to 31/03/2019, hence the books of accounts are considered up to 31/08/2019 and the bank transactions up to August 19. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.
